WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.897
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.364 --> 01:37.908
=Episode 4=

01:46.160 --> 01:48.201
(Lu Changfu will soon
assume his office.)

01:48.641 --> 01:49.600
(He is a wicked guy.)

01:50.121 --> 01:52.440
(His crimes against Lishan mountain
are numerous.)

01:52.641 --> 01:54.281
(The emperor hates him to the core.)

01:54.641 --> 01:57.160
(Yet he can't move against him due to
the Empress Dowager and Marquis Muyang.)

01:59.681 --> 02:00.561
(Eight years ago)
Eight years ago,

02:00.841 --> 02:02.160
the late emperor passed away.

02:02.160 --> 02:03.200
The crown prince died.

02:03.841 --> 02:06.081
Empress Guo Jin sought
to ascend the throne.

02:06.241 --> 02:08.561
Back then, Lishan Academy
was the cultural heart of Dachu.

02:08.880 --> 02:11.081
(Lishan Academy)
Almost half of the officials were from it.

02:11.480 --> 02:14.121
My grandfather took a stand
by closing Lishan to compile books.

02:14.401 --> 02:16.281
Also, scholars at court echoed together.

02:16.640 --> 02:17.600
Empress Guo was mad.

02:18.281 --> 02:20.320
She sent troops to besiege it
under the guise of protection.

02:20.920 --> 02:23.480
Lishan has been isolated ever since.

02:23.880 --> 02:25.361
Also, Lishan's scholars at court

02:25.561 --> 02:28.432
were falsely accused by Lu Changfu
under various charges.

02:28.432 --> 02:29.801
Some were dismissed from office,

02:30.561 --> 02:31.681
imprisoned, or exiled.

02:32.160 --> 02:34.160
And some were tortured to death.

02:34.760 --> 02:36.640
Li, one more thing.

02:36.961 --> 02:39.801
I've found Wei Zhuang,
but I didn't reveal myself to him.

02:52.480 --> 02:57.241
- Bravo!
- Bravo!

02:57.720 --> 02:58.521
Get out!

02:59.121 --> 02:59.920
What's going on?

03:00.361 --> 03:01.640
What's wrong with you?

03:02.160 --> 03:03.281
Are you blind?

03:03.760 --> 03:04.640
I'm turning you in.

03:04.640 --> 03:05.561
No way.

03:05.561 --> 03:07.440
Look, I can't even get up.

03:07.440 --> 03:08.521
Just give me a break.

03:08.760 --> 03:10.121
All of you are witnesses.

03:11.040 --> 03:13.121
The guy from Caiying Shop is hurting me!

03:13.121 --> 03:14.880
- Ouch!
- Nonsense!

03:15.121 --> 03:19.121
It was you who bumped into me first,
causing me to accidentally break these.

03:19.121 --> 03:20.880
- It hurts!
- You're blackmailing me.

03:22.440 --> 03:23.281
Take the money and leave.

03:24.121 --> 03:24.841
I don't want it.

03:26.040 --> 03:28.121
- I want justice!
- Justice?

03:28.880 --> 03:30.440
You want more, don't you?

03:30.640 --> 03:31.801
You wretched person!

03:31.920 --> 03:33.001
I won't give you a penny.

03:34.121 --> 03:34.736
Go.

03:35.200 --> 03:36.121
Go get some money.

03:38.001 --> 03:39.880
This man is handicapped already.

03:40.281 --> 03:42.081
(Wei Zhuang, Lishan scholar)
He'll stoop to anything for money.

03:42.401 --> 03:43.121
Everyone.

03:43.480 --> 03:44.561
It's over now.

03:45.281 --> 03:46.401
Please leave.

03:52.521 --> 03:53.640
It hurts so much.

04:12.760 --> 04:13.921
(Zhuang.)

04:14.161 --> 04:15.361
Ye Li, come here.

04:15.361 --> 04:16.640
- Zhuang.
- What is it?

04:16.640 --> 04:18.681
I learned a new hand trick.
Let me show you.

04:18.681 --> 04:19.400
Sure.

04:25.640 --> 04:26.760
So wonderful!

04:27.241 --> 04:28.280
Very clever of you.

04:29.041 --> 04:30.801
- Doesn't it look like a little bird?
- Yes, it does.

04:44.880 --> 04:46.080
Why is he leaving?

04:46.080 --> 04:47.400
Alright, let's go.

04:47.400 --> 04:48.921
Get out of here.

05:05.721 --> 05:07.280
Why are you back so late?

05:07.280 --> 05:08.681
Did you buy medicine for mother?

05:10.161 --> 05:11.320
Mother.

05:16.320 --> 05:17.640
How could you be so careless?

05:18.001 --> 05:20.041
Do not touch hot water again.

05:24.280 --> 05:24.976
Don't be scared.

05:25.601 --> 05:30.280
(You have a talent for arithmetic.)

05:30.280 --> 05:30.681
(Xu Qingyun,
Headmaster of Lishan Academy)

05:30.681 --> 05:34.681
Though counting rods are small,
they can calculate everything.

05:35.200 --> 05:39.481
If you can uphold your true heart
and benefit people,

05:39.921 --> 05:40.721
in the future,

05:40.921 --> 05:44.721
you may well achieve remarkable things.

05:45.241 --> 05:46.041
Yes.

05:46.161 --> 05:47.241
I'll remember your words.

05:48.030 --> 05:51.152
(Lishan Academy)

05:51.280 --> 05:53.440
Alright, no need to see me off further.

05:53.520 --> 05:54.400
Go back quickly.

05:55.001 --> 05:56.161
Goodbye then.

05:56.561 --> 05:58.440
I'll come find you
once I leave the mountain.

05:59.001 --> 06:00.801
Sure. We have a deal.

06:00.840 --> 06:01.721
I'll be waiting.

06:01.760 --> 06:02.681
Wei Zhuang, time to go.

06:03.041 --> 06:03.960
Coming, Yuanfeng.

06:07.520 --> 06:08.361
I'm leaving, Ye Li.

06:13.640 --> 06:15.520
Goodbye, Ye Li.

06:47.801 --> 06:48.321
Your Highness.

06:48.321 --> 06:51.121
What song are you humming?
Never heard it before.

06:52.001 --> 06:53.440
I don't know either.

06:53.921 --> 06:55.721
My mother used to hum it often.

06:55.880 --> 06:57.121
Over time, I learned it myself.

06:57.880 --> 06:58.721
It sounds lovely.

06:59.001 --> 06:59.801
Your Highness.

07:02.880 --> 07:05.400
Your needlework is truly excellent.

07:06.921 --> 07:08.320
I spent eight years on Lishan.

07:08.681 --> 07:11.361
I made the clothes
for my grandfather and all the masters.

07:11.361 --> 07:13.520
How can you do chores?

07:13.520 --> 07:16.320
Qingshuang was with you.
Why didn't she do them?

07:16.880 --> 07:19.921
She couldn't manage alone,
so I had to help her.

07:22.320 --> 07:24.561
Your Highness,
what silk are you using here?

07:24.561 --> 07:25.561
The color is so lustrous.

07:25.561 --> 07:26.561
It's quite beautiful.

07:27.320 --> 07:28.241
Touch it.

07:30.361 --> 07:31.561
Soft and thin.

07:31.681 --> 07:33.041
And surprisingly, it's warm.

07:33.241 --> 07:36.681
This is flame-woven silk,
from silkworms unique to the southwest.

07:37.080 --> 07:39.121
They only spin their cocoons
under moonlight.

07:39.440 --> 07:42.121
Hundreds of silkworms
yield just one chi of it.

07:42.880 --> 07:46.320
The flame-woven silk traps body heat,

07:46.400 --> 07:47.840
keeping the wind and chill at bay.

07:47.880 --> 07:48.921
What a great thing.

07:49.121 --> 07:51.681
I never saw the masters using it before.

07:52.481 --> 07:53.801
It's indeed good.

07:53.840 --> 07:54.840
But there's a problem.

07:55.241 --> 07:56.640
It requires careful storage.

07:57.161 --> 08:00.280
Contact with phosphor powder
would set it ablaze.

08:00.481 --> 08:04.001
Something so dangerous
can't be for His Highness, right?

08:04.400 --> 08:06.640
Phosphor powder isn't exactly common.

08:07.080 --> 08:08.001
Besides,

08:08.041 --> 08:09.721
this robe isn't for His Highness.

08:10.481 --> 08:12.121
Not for His Highness?

08:13.121 --> 08:14.601
Then who is it for?

08:28.481 --> 08:29.520
Shall I deliver this?

08:34.064 --> 08:35.344
Your Highness, we're going in.

08:50.984 --> 08:51.743
Your Highness?

08:52.263 --> 08:53.344
What's wrong?

08:53.704 --> 08:54.503
Your Highness!

08:54.743 --> 08:55.584
Your Highness!

08:56.464 --> 08:57.464
Get the physician!

08:57.464 --> 08:58.184
Hurry!

09:00.743 --> 09:01.543
Your Highness!

09:02.344 --> 09:03.464
Your Highness, wake up!

09:04.584 --> 09:05.383
Your Highness!

09:05.984 --> 09:06.824
Go get the physician!

09:07.743 --> 09:08.543
Come on.

09:09.344 --> 09:10.143
Your Highness!

09:12.743 --> 09:13.360
Come on!

09:21.503 --> 09:22.448
Your Highness.

09:22.704 --> 09:23.704
Your Highness, wake up!

09:24.104 --> 09:24.783
Your Highness.

09:24.783 --> 09:26.344
Can you hear me, Your Highness?

09:26.623 --> 09:27.304
Your Highness?

09:27.664 --> 09:29.304
Are you hearing me, Your Highness?

09:29.983 --> 09:30.983
Wake up, Your Highness!

09:31.264 --> 09:31.863
Your Highness!

09:32.223 --> 09:32.823
Your Highness!

09:39.862 --> 09:47.664
♪In silence, figures fade away♪

09:48.622 --> 09:52.881
♪Those fallen into the abyss♪

09:53.480 --> 09:58.110
♪Hold my life that hangs by a thread♪

09:59.591 --> 10:06.480
♪If you treat pain as swallowed needles♪

10:06.983 --> 10:10.103
Xiuwen, Xiuyao! Unforgivable!

10:10.544 --> 10:12.743
Brutal beasts!

10:12.743 --> 10:15.103
Prince Ding committed treason
and escaped!

10:15.103 --> 10:17.144
His crimes are numerous!

10:17.144 --> 10:18.463
He disgraced his ancestors!

10:19.144 --> 10:20.743
It's unpardonable.

10:21.223 --> 10:23.904
He is disloyal, betraying his country!

10:24.463 --> 10:27.304
You rebel is shameless!

10:27.384 --> 10:30.223
You deserve painful death!

10:30.223 --> 10:31.944
You abandoned your father and ruler.

10:31.944 --> 10:34.384
(Mo Xiuyao, Mo Xiuwen)
You're a beast.

10:35.703 --> 10:37.223
The traitorous subject Mo Xiuwen

10:37.583 --> 10:38.583
entered the capital

10:38.823 --> 10:40.024
without permission,

10:40.264 --> 10:41.544
endangering the border cities.

10:42.184 --> 10:44.264
(Death)
He is convicted of treason

10:45.064 --> 10:46.463
and will be decapitated today.

10:48.355 --> 10:52.016
♪I would rather light a lamp♪

10:57.863 --> 11:01.463
(His younger brother, Mo Xiuyao,
served under Duke Hua,)

11:01.583 --> 11:03.144
(not a member of the Heiyun Cavalry.)

11:03.144 --> 11:04.463
(He's not involved in treason.)

11:04.463 --> 11:06.424
(Considering his past merits,)

11:06.424 --> 11:08.664
(he's exempted
from the collective punishment.)

11:23.743 --> 11:25.103
(Hearing of what happened,)

11:25.184 --> 11:27.144
(I know your brother
is falsely accused.)

11:27.863 --> 11:29.103
(He is convicted of treason.)

11:29.384 --> 11:31.623
(The world also sees you as a traitor.)

11:31.823 --> 11:33.144
(It's a huge crime,)

11:34.184 --> 11:35.384
(only dragging you down.)

11:35.863 --> 11:37.184
(Those who try to help)

11:37.784 --> 11:39.024
(also fear getting implicated.)

11:40.747 --> 11:44.325
♪Grant the living a glimmer of hope♪

11:45.328 --> 11:49.141
♪Ease the grief of the departed♪

11:53.863 --> 11:55.144
(We're innocent!)

11:55.664 --> 11:57.144
(I received the imperial order!)

11:57.863 --> 11:59.384
(The Heiyun Cavalry never rebelled!)

11:59.544 --> 12:00.424
(General!)

12:00.544 --> 12:02.384
(We can gladly die for our country.)

12:02.863 --> 12:04.463
(But we cannot die
under a false charge!)

12:04.904 --> 12:05.983
(- Traitor!
- Die, you traitor!)

12:05.983 --> 12:06.904
(Traitor!)

12:06.904 --> 12:07.904
(Kill him!)

12:10.168 --> 12:13.928
♪I would rather drain our hope♪

12:14.224 --> 12:24.550
♪Than survive temporarily for illusions♪

12:31.583 --> 12:32.823
You're awake, Your Highness!

12:42.064 --> 12:43.144
I'll get you water.

12:56.223 --> 12:57.144
The physician says

12:58.583 --> 12:59.904
your old injury is back.

13:00.703 --> 13:01.823
Qi and blood are stagnant,

13:02.103 --> 13:03.184
causing a fever.

13:04.503 --> 13:05.944
That's why you got sick.

13:07.064 --> 13:08.064
Will it kill me?

13:09.904 --> 13:11.103
Then it's not serious.

13:15.144 --> 13:16.703
Why is there smoke from the study?

13:17.064 --> 13:17.904
Go check it out!

13:17.904 --> 13:19.103
Is there a fire?

13:33.503 --> 13:34.863
Your Highness, what are you doing?

13:34.944 --> 13:36.463
Get out quickly. It's dangerous.

13:36.664 --> 13:37.784
Stay out of this.

13:37.784 --> 13:38.664
Get out.

13:39.088 --> 13:39.743
Hurry!

13:39.743 --> 13:40.623
Put out the fire.

13:40.623 --> 13:41.184
Hurry.

13:41.184 --> 13:41.823
Yes.

13:46.503 --> 13:47.424
What are you doing?

13:48.103 --> 13:48.904
Stop!

14:12.583 --> 14:14.424
Why are you still keeping those things?

14:16.304 --> 14:17.384
None of your business.

14:18.343 --> 14:21.544
Since we're married, I'm your family.

14:21.703 --> 14:23.424
You're trapped in that room.

14:23.544 --> 14:25.863
The entire household is also trapped
because of you.

14:26.424 --> 14:28.384
I was trapped on Lishan for many years.

14:28.703 --> 14:30.784
I'm tired of being locked up again.

14:32.064 --> 14:32.983
Then leave!

14:33.144 --> 14:34.024
The door is there.

14:34.583 --> 14:35.503
No one's stopping you.

14:36.024 --> 14:36.688
Get out.

14:36.823 --> 14:37.823
Get out now.

14:44.863 --> 14:46.184
I've just become married to you.

14:47.103 --> 14:48.264
So I've taken a vow

14:48.863 --> 14:50.463
to rebuild the family name

14:51.064 --> 14:52.264
and share weal and woe.

14:59.703 --> 15:01.424
You've truly lost your mind.

15:03.264 --> 15:04.384
Do you know

15:05.304 --> 15:07.463
why everyone, from the nobles

15:07.823 --> 15:09.264
to the common people,

15:09.904 --> 15:11.503
loves watching dramas?

15:11.904 --> 15:13.743
It's because the more the drama twists

15:13.983 --> 15:15.103
and becomes complicated,

15:15.823 --> 15:17.544
the more excited the viewers become.

15:22.944 --> 15:23.823
Mo Xiuyao,

15:24.944 --> 15:26.384
don't let your life

15:27.264 --> 15:29.264
become nothing but a show in their eyes.

15:53.743 --> 15:55.503
What took you so long?

15:55.503 --> 15:58.784
I need to go thank His Majesty
and Empress Dowager before court today.

15:58.863 --> 16:00.384
Sorry to keep you waiting.

16:00.784 --> 16:03.743
I went to get your new official robe.

16:10.103 --> 16:12.424
The workers from the imperial palace
are quite thoughtful.

16:12.703 --> 16:14.264
Knowing Huaixi is humid,

16:14.463 --> 16:16.983
they've specially
added an extra layer inside.

16:17.223 --> 16:18.904
It can keep the dampness at bay.

16:19.264 --> 16:20.103
From the palace?

16:20.304 --> 16:22.503
Aren't official robes made
by the Imperial Wardrobe Bureau?

16:22.784 --> 16:23.743
The servants said

16:23.743 --> 16:27.343
the deliverer was dressed differently
from the previous one from the Bureau.

16:27.544 --> 16:30.343
I guess your official robe
is bestowed by the palace.

16:31.583 --> 16:33.583
I do appreciate it.

16:35.463 --> 16:36.264
Enjoy your meal.

16:36.823 --> 16:37.623
Excuse me,

16:37.623 --> 16:39.384
two steamed buns and a bowl of porridge.

16:39.664 --> 16:40.863
Okay, just a moment.

16:40.863 --> 16:41.904
Serve the porridge.

16:41.904 --> 16:42.503
Sure.

16:45.664 --> 16:47.703
(If Lu Changfu takes over
as Military Governor of Huaixi,)

16:48.144 --> 16:49.384
(it'll be harder
to deal with Marquis Muyang.)

16:50.103 --> 16:51.463
(Since the Emperor has the same idea,)

16:51.944 --> 16:52.743
(Li,)

16:52.944 --> 16:54.103
(let's act accordingly.)

17:10.624 --> 17:11.344
Your Highness.

17:11.344 --> 17:12.543
I've bought breakfast.

17:12.584 --> 17:14.584
Why are you here so early today?

17:14.904 --> 17:16.864
Are you in a good mood?

17:19.223 --> 17:20.584
I saw a lucky star.

17:21.023 --> 17:22.223
It's auspicious.

17:22.664 --> 17:23.824
Good fortune will come soon.

17:37.144 --> 17:39.063
I'll depart tomorrow

17:39.144 --> 17:40.864
to take up office in Huaixi.

17:41.144 --> 17:42.824
I came to express my gratitude

17:42.904 --> 17:44.144
for Your Majesty's trust

17:44.144 --> 17:45.664
and Your Grace's kindness.

17:45.864 --> 17:47.664
May Your Majesty be healthy.

17:47.743 --> 17:49.344
May our nation prosper.

17:49.424 --> 17:51.864
May Your Grace be healthy.

17:52.344 --> 17:56.223
If every court official
is as loyal and dedicated as you,

17:56.543 --> 17:57.463
doing their jobs

17:57.743 --> 17:58.824
faithfully

17:58.944 --> 18:01.104
and sincerely within boundaries,

18:01.904 --> 18:05.384
our nation will surely be prosperous

18:05.384 --> 18:06.664
and everlasting.

18:08.743 --> 18:09.543
Lu Changfu.

18:10.503 --> 18:12.223
I'll expect your achievements.

18:13.023 --> 18:15.584
I will do my best

18:15.584 --> 18:18.023
and shall not disappoint Your Majesties.

18:31.783 --> 18:32.584
Military Governor Lu.

18:32.584 --> 18:33.303
Hello.

18:33.303 --> 18:33.944
Congratulations!

18:37.263 --> 18:38.463
Military Governor Lu.

18:39.344 --> 18:41.223
Congratulations, General Lu.

18:41.463 --> 18:42.144
No.

18:42.144 --> 18:43.463
Military Governor Lu.

18:45.223 --> 18:46.023
Zhang.

18:46.023 --> 18:47.983
I'll head for Huaixi tomorrow.

18:47.983 --> 18:50.263
Hope you'll work well
for Marquis Muyang.

18:51.424 --> 18:52.223
Military Governor Lu.

18:52.303 --> 18:54.023
That is what I should do.

18:54.023 --> 18:55.384
You can set your mind at ease.

18:56.023 --> 18:57.584
By working for Marquis Muyang,

18:57.584 --> 18:59.023
you'll have a good future

18:59.023 --> 19:00.904
very soon.

19:00.904 --> 19:03.023
I hope so then.

19:04.944 --> 19:06.223
Take care, Military Governor Lu.

19:06.223 --> 19:06.904
Goodbye.

19:07.503 --> 19:09.063
Goodbye.

19:13.063 --> 19:13.664
Forgive me.

19:13.664 --> 19:14.184
How dare you!

19:14.184 --> 19:14.783
Forgive me.

19:14.783 --> 19:16.783
How dare you
bump into Military Governor Lu!

19:16.864 --> 19:18.023
Are you asking for death?

19:18.303 --> 19:21.384
He didn't mean it.
No need to be so harsh.

19:21.384 --> 19:22.543
Come on.

19:22.584 --> 19:23.184
Stand up.

19:25.424 --> 19:26.703
Greetings from Lishan Academy.

19:31.664 --> 19:33.223
Marquis Muyang.

19:37.063 --> 19:37.783
Marquis Muyang.

19:39.063 --> 19:40.904
I depart for Huaixi tomorrow.

19:41.104 --> 19:42.344
Once I've settled in there,

19:42.384 --> 19:43.624
I'll follow your instructions

19:43.664 --> 19:44.824
and rally.

19:45.023 --> 19:46.664
Await my good news.

19:47.904 --> 19:49.063
In Huaixi,

19:49.104 --> 19:50.864
you must be cautious.

19:50.904 --> 19:52.624
Don't act recklessly.

19:52.664 --> 19:53.424
Understood.

19:55.983 --> 19:56.543
What's wrong?

19:56.543 --> 19:57.063
Military Governor Lu.

19:57.063 --> 19:57.983
Your clothes!

19:57.983 --> 19:58.904
Smoke.

19:58.904 --> 19:59.664
They're smoking!

19:59.664 --> 20:00.424
What's happening?

20:00.983 --> 20:02.063
Why is it growing bigger?

20:12.904 --> 20:13.664
It's on fire!

20:14.144 --> 20:15.223
It's on fire!

20:20.263 --> 20:21.463
Marquis Muyang.

20:47.944 --> 20:49.063
(Eight years ago,)

20:49.063 --> 20:50.503
(my brother entered the capital
without orders.)

20:51.543 --> 20:54.104
(At that time,
I was serving under Duke Hua.)

20:54.944 --> 20:57.184
(Upon hearing the news,
I led troops northward.)

20:57.703 --> 21:00.104
(We fought against the Cangbei's forces
for over a month.)

21:38.664 --> 21:40.424
(The battle was fierce.)

21:40.503 --> 21:41.864
(Although we defeated the enemy,)

21:42.703 --> 21:44.783
(we lost over half of our soldiers.)

21:45.023 --> 21:45.783
Father!

21:45.783 --> 21:46.743
(My leg)

21:47.384 --> 21:50.344
(was injured in that battle.)

21:50.344 --> 21:51.023
Withdraw!

21:51.384 --> 21:52.864
Withdraw!

21:58.543 --> 22:00.944
(My brother
and his accompanying Heiyun Cavalries)

22:00.944 --> 22:02.543
(were all executed.)

22:04.023 --> 22:05.904
(The entire household was convicted.)

22:06.384 --> 22:08.144
(I was escorted back to the capital.)

22:09.904 --> 22:11.063
(On that day,)

22:11.904 --> 22:13.344
(I saw her again.)

22:18.104 --> 22:18.783
Mo Xiuyao?

22:19.223 --> 22:19.983
Mo Xiuyao!

22:20.703 --> 22:23.023
It's me, Ye Li! Do you remember me?

22:23.104 --> 22:24.023
You saved me before?

22:24.023 --> 22:24.944
Do you recall that?

22:25.344 --> 22:26.223
Make way!

22:26.463 --> 22:27.303
Do not approach!

22:27.783 --> 22:28.624
You traitor!

22:29.023 --> 22:29.783
Mo Xiuyao!

22:29.783 --> 22:30.503
Take this!

22:33.303 --> 22:34.263
Go die!

22:34.664 --> 22:35.944
Go die, you traitor!

22:36.344 --> 22:39.584
(When my brother entered the capital,
the former emperor had already died.)

22:40.463 --> 22:41.424
(His child ascended the throne.)

22:41.944 --> 22:43.543
(Empress Guo held court.)

22:44.424 --> 22:46.864
(My brother insisted he acted
by the late emperor's decree,)

22:47.184 --> 22:49.144
(but he never showed that decree.)

22:50.063 --> 22:53.424
(Marquis Muyang and others demanded
the execution of his entire lineage.)

22:54.023 --> 22:55.703
(I was condemned to death too.)

22:56.344 --> 22:59.144
(Duke Hua and military generals
pleaded for my life.)

22:59.703 --> 23:02.664
(The court officials debated endlessly.)

23:11.344 --> 23:12.743
(I was imprisoned)

23:13.303 --> 23:15.584
(and ignored at first.)

23:16.463 --> 23:18.463
(My leg injury remained untreated.)

23:19.703 --> 23:21.703
(Lu Changfu,
to curry favor with Marquis Muyang,)

23:22.624 --> 23:23.824
(bribed the prison guards.)

23:24.783 --> 23:25.864
(They didn't give me food or water.)

23:26.743 --> 23:27.703
(For the first few days,)

23:28.384 --> 23:31.144
(I lived on the pastries)

23:31.983 --> 23:33.144
(Ye Li had given me.)

23:35.344 --> 23:36.824
(That's how I survived.)

23:40.144 --> 23:41.104
(Six months later,)

23:41.824 --> 23:43.703
(I finally received the decree.)

23:43.864 --> 23:44.424
By the grace

23:44.424 --> 23:45.783
of heaven,

23:45.783 --> 23:47.104
I preside over all.

23:47.104 --> 23:50.263
Mo Xiuwen and the Heiyun Cavalry
are found guilty.

23:50.384 --> 23:53.384
Yet his younger brother, Mo Xiuyao,
served under Duke Hua.

23:53.584 --> 23:54.783
He was not involved in treason.

23:54.824 --> 23:56.503
Considering his past merits,

23:56.824 --> 23:58.783
he's exempted
from the collective punishment.

23:59.944 --> 24:01.503
You're quite lucky.

24:06.493 --> 24:08.011
(One month ago)

24:08.144 --> 24:10.023
(I waited for eight years.)

24:10.463 --> 24:13.424
(Finally, the current emperor decided
to eliminate Marquis Muyang,)

24:13.983 --> 24:15.743
(so I was secretly reinstated.)

24:25.463 --> 24:26.303
Xuanwu Gate.

24:26.463 --> 24:27.424
Seal the Zhuque alley.

24:27.664 --> 24:28.904
Ensure Yuan Fang's safety.

24:29.344 --> 24:30.144
Yes.

25:08.208 --> 25:08.880
Go.

25:31.944 --> 25:33.104
You were

25:33.503 --> 25:35.743
held captive by bandits and almost died.

25:36.303 --> 25:37.104
At that time,

25:37.263 --> 25:38.783
you sent a message to the capital

25:39.063 --> 25:40.783
about the progress on the weaponry case.

25:41.584 --> 25:42.944
Do you have evidence?

25:46.104 --> 25:49.543
I admire you. I would never betray you.

25:50.864 --> 25:53.144
Besides, given the feud
between Marquis Muyang and me,

25:53.624 --> 25:56.184
I will not collude with him.

25:57.063 --> 25:59.463
That's why His Majesty sent me.

26:01.824 --> 26:03.983
While I worked in Huaixi,

26:04.624 --> 26:05.664
indeed...

26:06.303 --> 26:07.104
Halt!

26:10.384 --> 26:13.223
By His Majesty's decree,
I'm here to get Military Governor Yuan.

26:14.543 --> 26:15.223
Eunuch Gao!

26:15.703 --> 26:16.813
We're not yet in the capital.

26:16.813 --> 26:19.344
Rashly taking him away may not be wise.

26:20.584 --> 26:22.743
I came by His Majesty's oral decree.

26:22.743 --> 26:25.104
Are you going
to defy the imperial order?

26:27.303 --> 26:28.023
Jin.

26:34.104 --> 26:34.904
Your Highness.

26:35.184 --> 26:36.864
His Majesty sent Eunuch Gao to take him.

26:47.824 --> 26:48.624
Prince Ding.

26:49.223 --> 26:50.703
This is His Majesty's order.

26:50.864 --> 26:52.624
His Majesty asks you to give him to me.

26:52.624 --> 26:56.144
His Majesty will
personally take care of the rest.

26:57.223 --> 26:59.904
I need to talk
to Military Governor Yuan now.

27:00.983 --> 27:02.864
His Majesty

27:03.223 --> 27:04.784
asks you

27:05.232 --> 27:07.503
to hand him over to me right now.

27:07.503 --> 27:09.184
(He bestowed upon me the blade)

27:09.384 --> 27:12.263
(yet always kept the scabbard
in his own hand.)

27:12.503 --> 27:14.463
Bride, please step out.

27:24.063 --> 27:26.144
Guests, take your seats.

27:28.703 --> 27:29.503
Your Highness.

27:32.263 --> 27:33.624
Go in through the secret passage.

27:34.104 --> 27:34.783
Yes.

27:45.263 --> 27:46.063
Change clothes!

27:55.664 --> 27:57.584
Prince Ding is occupied
with urgent matters now.

27:57.584 --> 27:58.824
Can't I just go in

27:58.904 --> 27:59.743
to see him?

28:02.424 --> 28:03.263
Hide!

28:20.864 --> 28:21.864
(After eight years,)

28:22.664 --> 28:24.104
(I saw her again.)

28:24.503 --> 28:27.344
(I still could see what she was like
as a kid.)

28:27.944 --> 28:30.463
(But I felt she had changed.)

28:30.543 --> 28:32.424
Today is our wedding day.

28:33.023 --> 28:35.783
You can't just stay here
copying scriptures all day, can you?

28:37.184 --> 28:38.624
But I haven't finished yet.

28:40.023 --> 28:41.144
Then do it later.

28:43.424 --> 28:44.223
Later,

28:44.864 --> 28:45.703
I'll help you.

28:48.743 --> 28:49.743
(She has grown up)

28:50.063 --> 28:50.904
(and grown taller.)

28:51.743 --> 28:53.344
(I saw the calluses on her fingers.)

28:53.584 --> 28:55.344
(She is less like an elegant lady.)

28:56.303 --> 28:57.904
(She no longer seems fragile,)

28:58.463 --> 29:01.783
(as if something pushes her forward.)

29:04.584 --> 29:05.983
(This was my wedding night,)

29:07.223 --> 29:10.424
(yet I had no heart
to play the role of a husband.)

29:18.144 --> 29:19.223
Your Highness.

29:19.223 --> 29:20.624
Military Governor Yuan was abducted

29:20.624 --> 29:22.104
on the capital outskirts.

29:22.384 --> 29:23.783
What?

29:25.743 --> 29:26.543
Find him!

29:26.824 --> 29:28.584
Dispatch more men. We must find him.

29:39.783 --> 29:41.144
Marquis Muyang must be behind it.

29:41.384 --> 29:44.063
Military Governor Yuan must have
had evidence of his arms smuggling.

29:44.864 --> 29:46.184
Now not only the evidence,

29:46.184 --> 29:47.472
even Military Governor Yuan...

29:53.023 --> 29:54.063
(Yuan Fang was abducted.)

29:54.864 --> 29:56.703
(He might have died.)

29:57.424 --> 29:59.303
(He escaped from Huaixi to Suixue Pass)

29:59.703 --> 30:01.263
(and tried to return to the capital.)

30:01.584 --> 30:03.743
(Yet he was gone
when he almost arrived.)

30:04.463 --> 30:05.543
(I was furious.)

30:07.104 --> 30:08.463
(Very much.)

30:38.263 --> 30:40.223
Where did His Highness rest last night?

30:40.543 --> 30:41.463
Your Highness.

30:41.703 --> 30:43.864
His Highness usually rests
in the bedroom.

30:43.864 --> 30:45.664
But last night, he stayed in the study.

30:47.783 --> 30:49.344
(But anger was futile.)

30:50.184 --> 30:51.503
(I had to move on.)

30:52.503 --> 30:53.743
(And in my life,)

30:55.223 --> 30:56.303
(a new presence appeared.)

30:59.144 --> 31:01.664
(When I was little, my mother asked me)

31:02.023 --> 31:04.384
(what sort of woman I wished to marry
when I was grown up.)

31:05.543 --> 31:06.664
(Back then, I thought)

31:07.503 --> 31:11.063
(if only my future wife could
be as elegant and good as my mother.)

31:11.983 --> 31:13.223
(When my brother married,)

31:13.664 --> 31:14.463
(I thought)

31:15.424 --> 31:16.503
(that to marry a wife)

31:16.743 --> 31:19.063
(as gentle and good as my sister-in-law)

31:19.783 --> 31:20.584
(would be fine too.)

31:22.063 --> 31:23.783
(Ye Li came
from a family in the capital.)

31:24.263 --> 31:26.384
(Her grandfather
was the Headmaster of Lishan Academy.)

31:27.184 --> 31:30.424
(I thought
she was a quiet, educated lady.)

31:31.144 --> 31:32.023
(But...)

31:52.424 --> 31:54.344
(She often ran past my doorway.)

31:56.344 --> 31:57.144
Jin.

31:59.543 --> 32:00.144
Your Highness.

32:00.624 --> 32:02.624
Does Her Highness have urgent business?

32:19.584 --> 32:20.703
(But I later discovered)

32:21.384 --> 32:23.104
(she didn't have urgent business to do.)

32:23.824 --> 32:25.263
(She ran like this every day.)

32:28.783 --> 32:29.584
Your Highness?

32:30.104 --> 32:31.584
You're up so early.

32:36.263 --> 32:37.543
(Later, three people ran)

32:37.664 --> 32:38.543
(together...)

32:38.703 --> 32:39.216
Your Highness.

32:39.216 --> 32:40.223
(every morning.)

32:43.344 --> 32:44.104
Your Highness.

32:44.104 --> 32:45.263
Your Highness, wait.

32:45.424 --> 32:46.344
Hold on.

32:46.584 --> 32:47.384
Your Highness.

32:48.912 --> 32:49.584
Your Highness.

32:49.783 --> 32:51.824
(She ran from Tuisi Pavilion
past the study)

32:51.824 --> 32:53.344
(and then circled back.)

32:53.783 --> 32:54.664
(The route unchanged.)

32:55.783 --> 32:59.144
(She said this helped her
absorb the spiritual energy)

32:59.543 --> 33:00.624
(and improve her health.)

33:03.503 --> 33:05.983
(But soon, she ran alone again.)

33:06.864 --> 33:07.664
Your Highness.

33:07.904 --> 33:11.703
Do you believe
she can absorb the spiritual energy

33:11.743 --> 33:12.664
and improve her health?

33:16.104 --> 33:17.023
Perhaps.

33:17.824 --> 33:19.424
(She would secretly drink liquor.)

33:19.864 --> 33:22.463
(The liquor smelled mild,
but was actually quite strong.)

33:22.824 --> 33:23.864
(She told others)

33:24.543 --> 33:27.864
(it was Qibao Tea from the border.)

33:27.864 --> 33:29.063
What are you drinking?

33:29.263 --> 33:30.503
Liquor?

33:33.104 --> 33:34.263
Alcohol leads to trouble.

33:34.503 --> 33:35.664
I do not drink alcohol.

33:36.263 --> 33:37.743
It's Qibao Tea.

33:38.063 --> 33:39.303
It promotes wellness.

33:40.976 --> 33:41.552
No...

33:48.944 --> 33:52.263
This smells like tea,

33:52.983 --> 33:54.624
but tastes somewhat...

33:58.743 --> 33:59.783
My alcohol!

34:03.784 --> 34:04.583
(Probably,)

34:04.904 --> 34:06.183
(she is that foolish.)

34:11.463 --> 34:12.143
So,

34:12.143 --> 34:14.784
what will these stone flowers
bloom into?

34:17.503 --> 34:18.904
(She has three pots of stones,)

34:19.344 --> 34:22.063
(claiming they are a gift
from Master Zhu.)

34:22.543 --> 34:24.344
(If they're watered daily)

34:24.623 --> 34:25.663
(and people talk to them,)

34:26.143 --> 34:28.183
(they would thrive.)

34:30.023 --> 34:32.864
(Only the two foolish maids of hers
seemed to believe it,)

34:33.304 --> 34:35.183
(looking after those three stones.)

34:35.623 --> 34:37.143
(All they think about was food.)

34:39.623 --> 34:40.704
(But watching her,)

34:41.264 --> 34:43.864
(I always felt she was lonely,)

34:44.583 --> 34:46.304
(just like those three pots of stones)

34:46.744 --> 34:48.424
(surrounded by colorful flowers)

34:48.824 --> 34:51.344
(yet destined never to bloom.)

34:56.344 --> 34:57.744
What are my grandfather,

34:58.063 --> 35:01.463
Master Zhu, and Master Ji doing now?

35:03.583 --> 35:05.063
My brother loves going to...

35:05.063 --> 35:06.663
(She often talked to herself.)

35:07.463 --> 35:08.784
(She stayed alone in her room,)

35:09.304 --> 35:12.344
(muttering to herself for a while.)

35:22.384 --> 35:23.183
Your Highness.

35:23.704 --> 35:25.623
Shall we play this less often?

35:26.344 --> 35:27.143
Why?

35:27.543 --> 35:29.384
You're constantly
showing off your fine legs.

35:29.384 --> 35:31.264
His Highness might see
and might be unhappy.

35:31.304 --> 35:32.744
Then he won't come here anymore.

35:33.623 --> 35:35.063
So what would make him happy?

35:35.904 --> 35:37.063
Copy sutras together?

35:38.704 --> 35:39.503
Don't worry.

35:39.704 --> 35:41.463
His Highness isn't that petty.

35:42.063 --> 35:42.904
Again.

35:47.663 --> 35:49.384
Your Highness, the ink is ready.

35:49.663 --> 35:50.744
May I go out?

35:52.663 --> 35:53.503
Go ahead.

35:55.784 --> 35:56.983
(But more often,)

35:57.784 --> 35:59.728
(she acted just as she did as a child.)

36:00.274 --> 36:01.864
(He talked a lot)

36:02.103 --> 36:03.784
(and lived happily and freely.)

36:03.784 --> 36:04.424
Are you alright?

36:04.543 --> 36:06.023
(And more people)

36:06.424 --> 36:07.623
(started to like her.)

36:08.063 --> 36:08.944
(She brought light)

36:09.344 --> 36:11.264
(into the eyes of many.)

36:13.424 --> 36:14.623
(After Yuan Fang died,)

36:15.063 --> 36:16.384
(His Majesty likely felt remorse)

36:17.063 --> 36:18.384
(and summoned me again.)

36:20.463 --> 36:21.103
Xiuyao.

36:29.183 --> 36:31.224
Due to my injured legs,
I cannot get up and bow.

36:31.503 --> 36:32.663
Please pardon me.

36:32.983 --> 36:34.543
Please, Xiuyao.

36:34.543 --> 36:36.583
We are cousins. Don't stand on ceremony.

36:37.744 --> 36:39.663
You look quite sharp,

36:39.663 --> 36:40.824
with an unyielding spirit.

36:40.824 --> 36:43.824
You're as heroic as before.

36:45.103 --> 36:46.424
I'm flattered, Your Majesty.

36:46.424 --> 36:49.744
I'm just an invalid
and don't deserve praise.

36:51.424 --> 36:54.304
What can I do for you, Your Majesty?

36:56.864 --> 36:59.023
A few days ago,
I heard of instability in Cangbei.

36:59.503 --> 37:00.864
It reminded me

37:00.864 --> 37:03.304
of how you defeated the enemy years ago.

37:03.304 --> 37:05.224
And again, I'm just an invalid.

37:05.463 --> 37:07.384
I don't deserve praise
from Your Majesty.

37:09.103 --> 37:11.023
You're displeased, aren't you?

37:12.344 --> 37:13.944
Don't blame me for not trusting you.

37:14.424 --> 37:16.784
Since I ascended the throne,

37:17.344 --> 37:19.063
I have had no one left to trust.

37:23.583 --> 37:25.744
I recognize your exceptional abilities.

37:26.143 --> 37:29.143
And I know how arduously you traveled
to retrieve Yuan Fang.

37:30.183 --> 37:33.103
Yet, because of my fear
of fully relying on anyone,

37:33.463 --> 37:35.384
I had Gao Wenhuan take Yuan Fang away.

37:36.063 --> 37:37.824
I intended to handle it personally.

37:42.583 --> 37:43.744
Unexpectedly...

37:46.143 --> 37:47.304
What's done is done.

37:48.103 --> 37:49.904
Now, I've come to understand

37:50.503 --> 37:52.424
that you traveled to Suixue Pass

37:52.784 --> 37:54.623
genuinely for my plan.

37:56.543 --> 37:58.023
I traveled far to Suixue Pass

37:59.143 --> 38:00.463
and rescued Yuan Fang.

38:02.864 --> 38:04.784
Your Majesty thinks I did that for you?

38:09.784 --> 38:11.583
Yuan Fang began
as a registrar in Yanzhou.

38:11.944 --> 38:14.424
In the fourth year of Jinghe,
he worked in Bianzhou.

38:14.623 --> 38:16.864
He got a top-grade official appraisal
in the fifth year of Jinghe.

38:18.264 --> 38:20.264
He deserved promotion
as an envoy for farming.

38:21.063 --> 38:22.463
But as an incorruptible official,

38:23.784 --> 38:26.224
he couldn't even afford the travel
to take up his post.

38:28.543 --> 38:30.103
Such a frail man,

38:31.463 --> 38:32.904
for the sake of the nation,

38:32.983 --> 38:35.623
threw himself headlong
into Marquis Muyang's lair in Huaixi.

38:36.784 --> 38:39.704
Do you know how he maneuvered
among the powerful locals?

38:40.264 --> 38:41.023
Do you know

38:41.143 --> 38:44.463
how he gathered evidence
when surrounded by the enemy?

38:45.328 --> 38:48.176
Do you know how he
depended on six severely injured guards

38:48.208 --> 38:49.503
desperately

38:49.704 --> 38:51.264
and was forced to flee to the border?

38:51.463 --> 38:53.224
How much blood was shed along the way?

38:53.503 --> 38:55.784
How many loyal men died?

38:57.944 --> 38:58.944
Do you even know?

38:59.784 --> 39:01.543
I know Yuan Fang endured hardship

39:02.063 --> 39:03.384
and struggled just to survive.

39:03.384 --> 39:04.304
He wanted to live

39:04.384 --> 39:05.944
not for himself,

39:07.224 --> 39:08.864
but to report what he knew,

39:08.864 --> 39:10.103
what he discovered,

39:10.143 --> 39:12.864
to hand over the evidence he held.

39:19.224 --> 39:21.583
To bring it into the light.

39:25.944 --> 39:27.623
Yet you overestimated yourself.

39:31.063 --> 39:33.063
You assumed you could protect Yuan Fang.

39:33.543 --> 39:35.744
But Yuan Fang died within half a day

39:37.983 --> 39:39.224
after you took him.

39:40.023 --> 39:41.983
He died within the capital confines.

39:44.704 --> 39:45.503
Your Majesty,

39:47.583 --> 39:49.103
have you ever reflected on it?

39:49.424 --> 39:50.583
You're out of line!

39:58.224 --> 39:58.983
Indeed.

39:59.543 --> 40:00.543
I was wrong.

40:01.304 --> 40:02.983
But are you blameless?

40:03.824 --> 40:06.904
If you are,
how was Suixue Pass breached?

40:07.744 --> 40:09.583
How did Xiuwen die?

40:13.424 --> 40:14.784
I remember now.

40:15.143 --> 40:16.824
Years ago, over a mere quarrel,

40:16.983 --> 40:19.143
you abandoned Xiuwen
and left the Heiyun Cavalry.

40:20.344 --> 40:21.864
Whenever I recall this,

40:22.063 --> 40:23.463
I feel profound regret.

40:23.944 --> 40:25.344
Had you been there,

40:25.864 --> 40:28.143
even with Xiuwen leading the army
to the capital,

40:28.583 --> 40:30.704
you could have
repelled Cangbei's attack.

40:30.983 --> 40:32.583
How could they succeed?

40:32.864 --> 40:34.583
So many people became homeless.

40:34.983 --> 40:37.103
Xiuwen would never die tragically.

40:41.824 --> 40:43.224
Don't look at me like that.

40:44.663 --> 40:45.824
I have no choice.

40:48.744 --> 40:49.543
Mo Xiuyao,

40:50.424 --> 40:51.983
you've made a mistake once before.

40:53.463 --> 40:55.384
This nation belongs to the Mo lineage.

40:56.463 --> 40:57.744
If you don't help me,

40:58.424 --> 40:59.744
letting others steal my throne,

41:00.583 --> 41:01.904
can you face our ancestors

41:02.424 --> 41:04.384
after your death?

41:04.744 --> 41:06.344
Can you face Xiuwen?

41:16.944 --> 41:17.663
Your Highness.

41:17.663 --> 41:18.704
Out!

41:21.748 --> 41:27.856
♪Only superficial peace remains♪

41:28.384 --> 41:31.384
(Xiuwen, Xiuyao! Unforgivable!)

41:31.904 --> 41:33.944
(Brutal beasts!)

41:33.944 --> 41:35.384
(Prince Ding committed treason
and escaped.)

41:35.384 --> 41:37.583
(She set my study aflame!)

41:37.583 --> 41:39.503
(The curses, the betrayal,)

41:39.704 --> 41:41.503
(and the silent injustice...)

41:41.704 --> 41:43.904
(All those once tortured me endlessly,)

41:43.904 --> 41:45.463
(along with the hate,)

41:45.583 --> 41:47.023
(were burned to ash.)

41:47.623 --> 41:50.143
(When light shone into my eyes,)

41:51.023 --> 41:53.983
(I finally saw an unquenched fire
in my chest!)

41:56.183 --> 41:57.023
Mo Xiuyao,

41:58.224 --> 41:59.583
don't let your life

42:00.463 --> 42:02.503
become nothing but a show in their eyes.

42:03.616 --> 42:06.115
♪Who hides in the shadows♪

42:07.460 --> 42:14.921
♪Reveal the world's true face♪

42:16.560 --> 42:20.816
♪The living, the dead♪

42:20.866 --> 42:24.976
♪Too many innocents♪

42:28.344 --> 42:29.784
Regarding the matter of Lu Changfu,

42:29.784 --> 42:31.583
I can help Your Majesty.

42:31.583 --> 42:34.143
But I have three demands.

42:34.774 --> 42:37.101
(Preview)

42:37.583 --> 42:38.424
Qingshuang,

42:38.904 --> 42:40.304
is Master Guan really that sort?

42:41.424 --> 42:42.503
I don't know.

42:45.143 --> 42:45.944
Qingshuang

42:46.143 --> 42:47.023
is here too?

42:52.784 --> 42:54.144
(Shende Shop)

42:54.744 --> 42:55.864
You need a steward?

42:56.944 --> 42:57.744
Yes.

42:59.264 --> 43:01.463
(We'll go meet
the Empress Dowager tomorrow,)

43:01.663 --> 43:03.224
(so I should rest early,)

43:03.663 --> 43:04.864
(regulate my breath)

43:05.344 --> 43:06.904
(and perform well tomorrow.)

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
